title: #202 - Danish & O'Neil & ME
description: Jeff Danis & Ryan O’Neill are writers, performers, and podcaster – we hang out in the Mancave drink White Wine, High Altitude Beers, more White Wine, Whiskey and talk about the East Coast/West Coast Comedy WAR, Freddy Soto, the conundrum that is Hasidic Ari Shaffir, wet dreams on horses, and my poetry period!
